## Typography Workflow

- [ ] 1. Understand the brand personality and creative direction
- [ ] 2. Define the typographic hierarchy — display, body, accent, UI
- [ ] 3. Select typefaces that match the brand and work across all required mediums
- [ ] 4. Establish sizing, weight, and spacing scales
- [ ] 5. Test readability across platforms and formats
- [ ] 6. Document typography rules in a type guide
- [ ] 7. Review against brand guidelines and flag any inconsistencies

## Key Inputs
- Brand/project: {{brand}}
- Typefaces currently in use: {{current_fonts}}
- Required platforms/formats: {{platforms}}
- Brand personality keywords: {{personality}}
- Readability requirements: {{readability}}
